CHROMA ATE INC (2360)  said unconsolidated sales
in May fell 30.39% to NT$391,223,000 from NT$562,013,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  5/2012           5/2011
Sales            391,223          562,013    
YOY%             -30.39%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           1,593,475        2,608,663   
YOY%             -38.92% 
=================================================================
 